Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.18,1:29:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次去哪呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Where to now?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.59,1:29:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本 美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Japan, States,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.02,1:29:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢去哪就去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} wherever you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.89,1:30:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.19,1:30:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别到时候连你的影子都找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I hope you won't leave me standing again
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.93,1:30:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗱 你乖乖的在清水湾码头等我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} We'll come pick you up as soon as we're finished
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.43,1:30:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们办完事立刻去找你 嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Dear, you be Clear Water Bay pier
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.80,1:30:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的要来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} You better!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.34,1:30:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 老爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Dad Dad
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.68,1:30:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儿子 画呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Son, where's the painting?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.28,1:31:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们父子三人不是要变成这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What happened to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.09,1:31:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不对呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.75,1:31:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远都不会忘记你的养育之恩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'll never forget you raised me, it's engraved in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.86,1:31:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们俩很乖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Jim, I know you are very filial,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.80,1:31:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想拿回那幅画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I just want my painting
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.80,1:31:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是把画还给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'll give you the painting,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.13,1:31:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就放我们一马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} but you have to let us go
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.43,1:31:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画是我的命根子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} That painting is my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.27,1:31:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们肯把画还我 等于放我一马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} if you give it back to me, I'll let you go
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.11,1:31:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好说 您真仁慈 谢谢您给我们自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} You're so kind, thanks for giving us freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.81,1:31:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更多谢您放我们一马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Especially this chance
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.81,1:31:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} The money?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.50,1:31:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你们养这么大 原来是养虎为患\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I raised both of you, but I never thought you turn out so cruel
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.81,1:31:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿回你们欠我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'll exterminate you
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.01,1:32:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} No please
