Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.70,1:33:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避弹衣 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} It's bullet proof vest, so what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.31,1:33:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事啊 哈哈你骗我啊 装瘸子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Nothing, but aren't you limped?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.78,1:33:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不装瘸子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} If I weren't limped,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.31,1:33:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会让我参加吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} you won't be with me
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.38,1:33:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不装瘸子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} If I weren't limped,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.78,1:33:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来老爸早就把我宰啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} when I came back, dad would have killed me
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.22,1:33:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是骗了很多你的感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Did I made you sad...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.66,1:33:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多的眼泪啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} and cry?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.29,1:33:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红豆那份怎么算啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What about Cherie?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.22,1:33:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会向她解释的 混球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'll explain to her
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.66,1:33:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老爸呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Where's dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.95,1:35:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的 真画在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} You bastard, where's the real painting?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.54,1:35:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他杀了 别弄坏那画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Kill him, don't spoil the painting
