Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.70,1:38:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么多A士 你还有A士吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} So many Ace, you must have AIDS
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.10,1:38:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有你多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Not as many as you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.27,1:38:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你查查看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'll check for you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.21,1:38:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的 我的衣服好贵的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Shit, you spoil my best suit
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.13,1:39:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 香蕉水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} It's corrosive fluid
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.20,1:39:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我喝了香蕉水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I drank the corrosive fluid
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.38,1:39:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Call the ambulance
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.90,1:40:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善哉 善哉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Don't panic,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.54,1:40:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就跟你说了不要玩火嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I asked you not to play with fire
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.81,1:40:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫消防车来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Call the fire truck
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.90,1:40:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.67,1:40:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事干爹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What you want, dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.60,1:40:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上去拿画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Get the painting!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.61,1:40:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画上有电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} But it's wired
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.21,1:40:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Go on
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.94,1:42:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救火呀 快来救火呀 画完啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Put it out, it's gone, it's gone
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.08,1:42:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快来救火呀 快救火呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} The painting is gone, put it out
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.98,1:42:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完啦 全完啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Put it out, put it out, oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.82,1:42:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 怎么样 很难受是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Dad, how is painful?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.59,1:42:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 先坐下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Take a rest
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.46,1:42:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扶你 来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Let me help you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.60,1:42:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个想杀我 没那么容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} You two want to kill me, not so easy
