Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.34,1:42:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Alright, alright
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.37,1:42:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟老爸好好聊一聊 交给你啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Go and talk to dad for a while
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.14,1:42:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每部电影的结尾都是坏人绳之于法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} All movies have the bad guys caught at the end
