Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.61,1:42:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包涵包涵 啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Smile, hey
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.05,1:42:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Don't move
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.66,1:42:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么走啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} You intend to leave like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.46,1:42:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都大义灭亲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} We caught him for justice
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.33,1:42:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您又遂了心愿 不走干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} And your wish come true, what's the point of staying?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.40,1:42:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Clean this mess up first
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.70,1:42:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.63,1:42:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要这么走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'm a police officer
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.50,1:43:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我不是很没面子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I can't let you go, that's illegal
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.30,1:43:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打不下手啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I can't do this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.97,1:43:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 儿子打老爸 天打雷劈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Patricide is punishable by death
