Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.52,1:43:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Hey, hit him
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.42,1:43:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来打吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Go on, hit
