Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.85,1:44:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Take care
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.48,1:44:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.35,1:44:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦 祝你们俩个春梦了无痕吶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} I'm leaving, I wish you all the best
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.76,1:45:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿贵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Joe
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.66,1:45:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是怎么样啊 怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Yes, well, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.86,1:45:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一定要留你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} We don't mean you must stay
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.29,1:45:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你说过的话要算数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} But don't you think a promise must be kept
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.10,1:45:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过什么话啦我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} What did I promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.93,1:45:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答应过做我孩子的干爹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} You promised to be godfather to our kids, remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.93,1:45:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是随便那么一说嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} That was a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.67,1:45:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且馅儿都有啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Well, Cherie is pregnant now
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.20,1:45:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真难听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Hey, stop that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.50,1:45:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么不小心哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Mustn't forget the condoms!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.21,1:45:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来不来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.37,1:45:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别烦我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Sure you don't want to come
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.51,1:45:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 开船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Alright, cast off
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.88,1:45:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 等一等 我来解缆绳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Stop, wait for me
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.85,1:45:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这幅画呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} So where is the painting?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.05,1:45:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完璧归赵啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Back home
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.81,1:45:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做饭去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12} Go back to work.
